      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/26/multiple-people-could-face-charges-in-matthew-perrys-death-reports.webp" alt="Multiple people could face charges in Matthew Perry's death: reports"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Multiple people could face charges in Matthew Perry's death: reports</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Just last month, law enforcement officials revealed they were launching a criminal investigation to look into how Perry obtained and consumed so much of ketamine.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/26/multiple-people-could-face-charges-in-matthew-perrys-death-reports/"  >(Christine Samra, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:52:25 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:52:25 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Matt Jaworowski, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/27/comet-not-seen-since-1956-set-to-fly-by-earth.webp" alt="Comet not seen since 1956 set to fly by Earth"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Comet not seen since 1956 set to fly by Earth</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Stargazers will want to keep a close eye on the sky in the coming days. A comet with a 69-year orbit is set to pass by Earth.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/27/comet-not-seen-since-1956-set-to-fly-by-earth/"  >(Matt Jaworowski, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:00:00 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:00:00 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MARK THIESSEN, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/27/wind-driven-wildfire-spreads-outside-a-central-oregon-community-and-prompts-evacuations.webp" alt="Wind-driven wildfire spreads near popular central Oregon vacation spot and prompts evacuations"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Wind-driven wildfire spreads near popular central Oregon vacation spot and prompts evacuations</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A wildfire in Oregon’s high desert, near the popular vacation destination of Bend, grew rapidly Wednesday, and officials urged the continued evacuations of hundreds of homes in the area best known for its microbreweries, hiking, river rafting and skiing on nearby Mount Bachelor.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/27/wind-driven-wildfire-spreads-outside-a-central-oregon-community-and-prompts-evacuations/"  >(MARK THIESSEN, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:54:44 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:54:44 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JUAN A. LOZANO and MICHAEL GRACZYK, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/27/texas-inmate-facing-execution-for-2001-fatal-shooting-as-his-lawyers-argue-hes-no-longer-a-danger.webp" alt="Texas man executed for 2001 abduction and killing of 18-year-old woman"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Texas man executed for 2001 abduction and killing of 18-year-old woman</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      HUNTSVILLE, Texas (AP) — A Texas man who admitted he kidnapped, sexually assaulted and fatally shot an 18-year-old woman in 2001 was executed Wednesday evening. Ramiro Gonzales, 41, was pronounced dead at 6:50 p.m.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/27/texas-inmate-facing-execution-for-2001-fatal-shooting-as-his-lawyers-argue-hes-no-longer-a-danger/"  >(JUAN A. LOZANO and MICHAEL GRACZYK, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:05:13 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:05:13 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Rich Johnson, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
