      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/27/kennedy-joins-newsnations-debate-coverage.webp" alt="Robert F. Kennedy Jr. to join NewsNation debate coverage"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Robert F. Kennedy Jr. to join NewsNation debate coverage</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Kennedy plans to comment on the Biden-Trump debate in a livestream during the debate, then join NewsNation’s post-debate coverage.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/27/kennedy-joins-newsnations-debate-coverage/"  >(Rich Johnson, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 25 Jun 2024 16:06:50 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 25 Jun 2024 16:06:50 +0000">
