      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/25/sunscreen-doesnt-cause-cancer-despite-tiktok-claims-doctors.webp" alt="Sunscreen doesn't cause cancer, despite TikTok claims: doctors"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Sunscreen doesn't cause cancer, despite TikTok claims: doctors</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Influencers on social media are claiming that wearing sunscreen causes cancer rather than preventing it .
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/25/sunscreen-doesnt-cause-cancer-despite-tiktok-claims-doctors/"  >(Anna Kutz, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:35:30 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:35:30 +0000">
