      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/26/california-dmv-introduces-spanish-version-of-online-course.webp" alt="California DMV introduces Spanish version of online course"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">California DMV introduces Spanish version of online course</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The California Department of Motor Vehicles has added an online fail-safe eLearning course in Spanish, allowing Spanish-speaking Californians to renew their driver's license without having to visit a DMV office.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/26/california-dmv-introduces-spanish-version-of-online-course/"  >(Jeremiah Martinez, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
