      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/26/flatulent-cows-and-pigs-will-face-a-carbon-tax-in-denmark-a-world-first.webp" alt="Gassy cows and pigs will face a carbon tax in Denmark, a world first"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Gassy cows and pigs will face a carbon tax in Denmark, a world first</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The aim is to reduce Danish greenhouse gas emissions by 70% from 1990 levels by 2030, said Taxation Minister Jeppe Bruus.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/26/flatulent-cows-and-pigs-will-face-a-carbon-tax-in-denmark-a-world-first/"  >(JAN M. OLSEN, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:37:02 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:37:02 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Rod Mcguirk, Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/25/australian-leaders-cautiously-welcome-expected-plea-that-could-bring-wikileaks-founder-assange-home.webp" alt="Australian leaders cautiously welcome expected plea that could bring WikiLeaks founder Assange home"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Australian leaders cautiously welcome expected plea that could bring WikiLeaks founder Assange home</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Australian leaders are cautiously welcoming an expected plea agreement that could set free WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/25/australian-leaders-cautiously-welcome-expected-plea-that-could-bring-wikileaks-founder-assange-home/"  >(Rod Mcguirk, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:00:11 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:00:11 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/26/coup-attempt-underway-in-bolivia-as-president-urges-people-to-mobilize-against-it.webp" alt="Bolivian general arrested after apparent failed coup attempt as government faces new crisis"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Bolivian general arrested after apparent failed coup attempt as government faces new crisis</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Armored vehicles rammed into the doors of Bolivia’s government palace Wednesday as President Luis Arce said the country faced an attempted coup and urged people to mobilize.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/26/coup-attempt-underway-in-bolivia-as-president-urges-people-to-mobilize-against-it/"  >(Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:29:39 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:29:39 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Garrett Phillips, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/24/apple-becomes-first-target-of-eus-new-digital-competition-rules-aimed-at-big-tech.webp" alt="Apple becomes first target of EU's new digital competition rules aimed at big tech"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Apple becomes first target of EU's new digital competition rules aimed at big tech</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      European Union regulators are accusing Apple of breaking new rules on digital competition by imposing rules in its App Store marketplace that prevent app makers from pointing users to cheaper options on other venues.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/24/apple-becomes-first-target-of-eus-new-digital-competition-rules-aimed-at-big-tech/"  >(Garrett Phillips, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 21:51:22 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 21:51:22 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Brad Dress, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/26/netanyahu-biden-feud-war-gaza.webp" alt="Netanyahu picks fight with Biden over arms transfers as US election heats up"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Netanyahu picks fight with Biden over arms transfers as US election heats up</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu has escalated his feud with President Biden over the war in Gaza, accusing him of holding back arms transfers in a highly public dispute, which analysts say is meant to pressure and potentially even embarrass the White House ahead of the U.S. elections.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/26/netanyahu-biden-feud-war-gaza/"  >(Brad Dress, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:31:53 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:31:53 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="EVELYNE MUSAMBI, Associated Press, KREX 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/27/kenyan-police-fire-blanks-to-disperse-protesters-hours-after-parliament-breached.webp" alt="Kenya's president says he won't sign the finance bill that led protesters to storm the parliament"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Kenya's president says he won't sign the finance bill that led protesters to storm the parliament</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NAIROBI, Kenya (AP) — Kenya's president said Wednesday he won't sign into law a finance bill proposing new taxes that prompted thousands of protesters to storm the parliament the previous day, leaving several people killed as police opened fire.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/27/kenyan-police-fire-blanks-to-disperse-protesters-hours-after-parliament-breached/"  >(EVELYNE MUSAMBI, Associated Press, KREX 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:58:12 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:58:12 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Tara Suter, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/27/harvard-jewish-muslim-students-discriminated.webp" alt="Harvard task forces finds both Jewish and Muslim students were discriminated"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harvard task forces finds both Jewish and Muslim students were discriminated</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Two Harvard University task forces aimed at tackling antisemitism and anti-Muslim and anti-Arab bias released preliminary recommendations Wednesday, finding discrimination faced by both Muslim and Jewish students.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/27/harvard-jewish-muslim-students-discriminated/"  >(Tara Suter, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
