    <h3 itemprop="headline">SingleStoreDB Leverages Apache Iceberg for Seamless Data Integration</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      In response to growing customer demand, SingleStore has integrated Apache Iceberg into its SingleStoreDB offering, empowering enterprises to effortlessly access and utilize data stored in data lakehouses.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/26/singlestoredb-joins-the-apache-iceberg-bandwagon/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
