           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Giant underwater US drone&#160;pictured in satellite images</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The technology is part of what some call “sea drone warfare” — something America’s adversaries are also plotting for.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/26/giant-underwater-us-drone-picture-manta-ray/"  >(Nancy Loo, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
