    <h3 itemprop="headline">Isaiah Collier drafted by Jazz with 29th pick</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SALT LAKE CITY (ABC4 Sports) - The Utah Jazz continued to follow their first round trend, drafting their fifth 19-year-old in the first round in the last two years with the selection of USC guard Isaiah Collier with the 29th overall pick in the NBA Draft Wednesday night.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/27/jazz-select-usc-guard-isaiah-collier-with-29th-pick/"  >(Dana Greene, ABC 4)</a>
