    <h3 itemprop="headline">House hearing exposes Biden FDA 'politicization,' fallout of rushed COVID vaccine approval for kids, military</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      House Republicans heard from doctors and other witnesses about the “politicization&quot; of the FDA under the Biden administration regarding the COVID vaccine.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/26/house-hearing-exposes-biden-fda-politicization-fallout-rushed-covid-vaccine-approval-kids-military/"  >(Fox News)</a>
