  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/26/texas-set-to-execute-ramiro-gonzales-for-2001-murder.webp" alt="Texas executes Ramiro Gonzales for 2001 murder"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Texas executes Ramiro Gonzales for 2001 murder</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Gonzales, who was on death row for the rape and murder of Bridget Townsend in Medina County, is the second person to be executed in Texas this year.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/26/texas-set-to-execute-ramiro-gonzales-for-2001-murder/"  >(Texas Tribune, By William Melhado And Kayla Guo, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 15:00:00 +0000">
